{"title":"悼念","authors":["高光"],"dates":[{"year":1989,"month":4,"day":25}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"悼念"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您曾攀登昆仑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"头上却没有虚幻的光环"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您也执掌中华"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"面部竟不显神的威严"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您的心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如同袒裸的日月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喜怒哀乐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"恰似无羁的潮汐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您的话语"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胜过弦上的箭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胸中一旦发射"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"决无回旋转弯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一腔炽热，销溶掉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难以计数的镣铐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"双臂潇洒，放飞出"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亿万友爱的信鸽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有人把您当作"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顶礼膜拜的救世主"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您是我们的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"知冷知热"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"问饥问渴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"情同骨肉的兄长"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鞠躬尽瘁的老师"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您以生命写就的教案"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"启迪世世代代"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跋山涉水地寻觅"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生命的价值"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和人类的尊严"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我在自己的屋檐下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"垂首扪心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深深地哀悼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不再流酸涩的泪水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（我的热泪早已在"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丙辰清明流干"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老眼变成龟裂的枯潭）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不再写哀怨的挽幛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（不论是白纸黑字"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还是蓝纸血字，都无以表达"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心灵的震颤）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不再扎苍白的花圈"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（瞑目以后，忠诚和奸佞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"善者与恶棍，都能享用"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这类僵死的艺术）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我只有清流般的悼念"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"献给您"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万瓣心香"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千叶肝胆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"１９８９年４月１５日夜"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}